        "plotShort": {
            "plainText": "Stations of the Cross (film)\r\nStations of the Cross (German: Kreuzweg) is a 2014 German drama film directed by Dietrich Br\u00fcggemann. The film had its premiere in the competition section of the 64th Berlin International Film Festival, where it won the Silver Bear for Best Script.",
            "html": "<h2>Stations of the Cross (film)</h2><p>Stations of the Cross (German: Kreuzweg) is a 2014 German drama film directed by Dietrich Br\u00fcggemann. The film had its premiere in the competition section of the 64th Berlin International Film Festival, where it won the Silver Bear for Best Script.</p>"
